# Credentials for the nightly auto-curation bot (curation/AUTOMATED_CURATION.md).
#
# Copy this file to `.env` (right here, in curation/) and fill in real values.
# `curation/.env` is gitignored — never commit real keys.
#
#   cp curation/.env.example curation/.env && $EDITOR curation/.env
#
# Commands that need a secret are run through `curation/with-secrets.sh`, which
# loads this file, verifies the *named* secret(s) are present, and errors out if
# any is missing — e.g.
#   bash curation/with-secrets.sh GEMINI_API_KEY -- python .claude/skills/nano-banana-pro/generate.py …
#   bash curation/with-secrets.sh CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN -- npx --yes wrangler r2 object put …

# --- Google Gemini API (image + video generation) ------------------------
# Used by the nano-banana-pro and veo3-video-gen skills (google-genai SDK reads
# GEMINI_API_KEY from the env). Get one at https://aistudio.google.com/apikey . Required.
GEMINI_API_KEY=

# Optional model overrides (sane defaults baked into the skills):
# GEMINI_IMAGE_MODEL=gemini-3-pro-image
# VEO_MODEL=veo-3.1-generate-preview

# --- Cloudflare R2 (uploading the MP4) -----------------------------------
# A Cloudflare API token with R2 read/write on the `screensaver-assets` bucket.
# Needed so `wrangler` works non-interactively in the nightly run.
# Create at https://dash.cloudflare.com/profile/api-tokens . Required for upload.
CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN=
# Only needed if your token spans multiple accounts:
# CLOUDFLARE_ACCOUNT_ID=
